Red Dawn
========

Red Dawn is a system to store various email abuse reports sent in ARF. It is organized in such a way that fraudulent emails can be easily selected, sorted and reported back to the resource owners. For instance it can be used to receive DMARC failure reports.

How to install
==============

This requires python, flask and mysql server.

1) create the database using the forensic.sql file
2) run the web server forensic.py
3) install in a cron job the script forensic-mysql.py
4) send failure reports to the appropriate mailbox that forensic-mysql.py will read